She jumped back as quickstrike snapped his claw at her.  She looked 
at Quickstrike with a frown.  She nodded her head, and acknowlaged 
his intention of telling her to chill.  She Stood back and kept a 
sharp eye on Megatron.  She wasn't going to say anything t Megatron 
unless absolutely nessassary.  She was afraid she would say something 
that might set the fireworks off.
